languages.text: {n}Ответив возмущенным взглядом, Хейнрикс оскорбленно цедит:{/n} "И не собирался".
{n}Visibly offended, Heinrix looks back at you coldly and mutters,{/n} "I had no intention of complying."
languages.original_text: {n}Ответив возмущенным взглядом, Хейнрикс оскорбленно цедит:{/n} "И не собирался".

traits.locale_text: {n}Staring back with a gaze full of rage, Heinrix hurtfully speaks through his clenched teeth:{/n} "And never intended to do so."

languages.original_text: {n}Visibly offended, Heinrix looks back at you coldly and mutters,{/n} "I had no intention of complying."

languages.text: {n}Claramente ofendido, Heinrix te lanza una mirada fría y murmura:{/n} «No tenía intención de obedecer».
languages.original_text: {n}Visibly offended, Heinrix looks back at you coldly and mutters,{/n} "I had no intention of complying."

traits.locale_text: {n}Con una mirada llena de ira, Heinrix, dolido, esputa con la mandíbula apretada:{/n} «Y nunca tuve intención de hacerlo».
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}很显然，你的话冒犯到了海因里希。他回过头，冷冷地看着你，低声开了口。{/n}“我根本没打算听他的。”
languages.original_text: {n}Visibly offended, Heinrix looks back at you coldly and mutters,{/n} "I had no intention of complying."

traits.locale_text: {n}海因里希瞪着你，目光中充满了愤怒。他咬紧牙关，以痛苦的声音开了口。{/n}“我根本没打算听他的。”
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}Heinrix blickt dich sichtlich beleidigt mit kalten Augen an und murmelt:{/n} "Ich hatte nie vor, zu gehorchen."
languages.original_text: {n}Visibly offended, Heinrix looks back at you coldly and mutters,{/n} "I had no intention of complying."

traits.locale_text: {n}Heinrix starrt mit einem zornerfüllten Blick zurück und sagt dann durch seine zusammengebissenen Zähne:{/n} "Und es war auch nie beabsichtigt."
traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: {n}目に見えて気分を害したハインリックスは冷徹にあなたを見返し、つぶやいた。{/n}「我は従うつもりはなかった」
languages.original_text: {n}Visibly offended, Heinrix looks back at you coldly and mutters,{/n} "I had no intention of complying."
